<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.3/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet"
    integrity="sha384-QWTKZyjpPEjISv5WaRU9OFeRpok6YctnYmDr5pNlyT2bRjXh0JMhjY6hW+ALEwIH" crossorigin="anonymous" />
  <link rel="stylesheet"
    href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/bootstrap-icons/1.5.0/font/bootstrap-icons.min.css" />

  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/assets/styles/main.css">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/assets/styles/privacy-policy.css">
  <title>Website Privacy Information</title>
</head>

<body class="footer-padding">
  <%- include('./partials/loading-screen') %>
  <%- include('./partials/search-popup') %>

  <div class="site-content">
    <%- include('./partials/navigation') %>

    <main class="container-fluid mb-5">
      <section class="container py-5">
        <div class="row mb-4">
          <div class="col text-center">
            <h1 class="display-4 fw-bold">Privacy Notice</h1>
            <p class="lead">This privacy policy outlines how we collect, use, and protect your personal information when you use this website.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="row mb-4">
          <div class="col-md-12">
            <div class="card p-4 mb-4 shadow-sm">
              <h2 class="h4 fw-bold">Consent to Use Data</h2>
              <p>By accessing and using this website, you consent to the collection, storage, and processing of your personal information as outlined in this privacy policy.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="row mb-4">
          <div class="col-md-12">
            <div class="card p-4 mb-4 shadow-sm">
              <h2 class="h4 fw-bold">Providing Your Information</h2>
              <p>While you are not required to provide personal details, failure to do so may limit your ability to access certain features or services on the site.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="row mb-4">
          <div class="col-md-12">
            <div class="card p-4 mb-4 shadow-sm">
              <h2 class="h4 fw-bold">Voluntary Disclosure</h2>
              <p>By submitting your information, you do so voluntarily and agree to allow us to use this data in compliance with relevant privacy laws and our privacy policy.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="row mb-4">
          <div class="col-md-12">
            <div class="card p-4 mb-4 shadow-sm">
              <h2 class="h4 fw-bold">How We Use Your Data</h2>
              <p>We may utilize your data for the following purposes:</p>
              <ul>
                <li>Enable you to access and use the website's features;</li>
                <li>Enhance, update, and optimize the website;</li>
                <li>Personalize content and services based on your preferences;</li>
                <li>Contact you when necessary;</li>
                <li>Send promotional materials, product offers, and updates;</li>
                <li>Aggregate and analyze data to improve services;</li>
                <li>Monitor website usage, including cookies and tracking technologies;</li>
                <li>Protect our rights and interests, and comply with legal requirements;</li>
                <li>Other purposes as stipulated by law or our privacy policy.</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="row mb-4">
          <div class="col-md-12">
            <div class="card p-4 mb-4 shadow-sm">
              <h2 class="h4 fw-bold">Data Protection</h2>
              <p>We are committed to protecting your data and ensuring it is not sold or shared without your consent, except under specific circumstances like legal obligations or business transactions.</p>
              <ul>
                <li>In compliance with applicable laws;</li>
                <li>To resolve disputes or handle complaints;</li>
                <li>For legal or regulatory purposes;</li>
                <li>In case of mergers, acquisitions, or bankruptcy;</li>
                <li>To third-party service providers supporting website operations.</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="row mb-4">
          <div class="col-md-12">
            <div class="card p-4 mb-4 shadow-sm">
              <h2 class="h4 fw-bold">Business Closure</h2>
              <p>If our business ceases operations, your information will still be retained and processed according to applicable laws.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="row mb-4">
          <div class="col-md-12">
            <div class="card p-4 mb-4 shadow-sm">
              <h2 class="h4 fw-bold">Data Transfer</h2>
              <p>Your personal information may be transferred to other jurisdictions for storage or processing. In such cases, we will ensure that appropriate safeguards are in place to protect your data.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="row mb-4">
          <div class="col-md-12">
            <div class="card p-4 mb-4 shadow-sm">
              <h2 class="h4 fw-bold">Reviewing and Correcting Information</h2>
              <p>You may review your personal information stored in our system. If any data is incorrect, outdated, or incomplete, you can request that it be corrected or deleted.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="row mb-4">
          <div class="col-md-12">
            <div class="card p-4 mb-4 shadow-sm">
              <h2 class="h4 fw-bold">Marketing Communications</h2>
              <p>If you no longer wish to receive marketing communications, please notify us, and we will ensure that you are removed from our distribution lists as per the applicable laws.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="row mb-4">
          <div class="col-md-12">
            <div class="card p-4 mb-4 shadow-sm">
              <h2 class="h4 fw-bold">Security Measures</h2>
              <p>We implement reasonable measures to safeguard your personal data. However, we cannot guarantee that unauthorized third parties will not gain access to this data. We are not responsible for any damages that may arise due to breaches.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <%- include('./partials/footer') %>
      </section>
    </main>
  </div>

  <!-- MODALS -->
  <%- include('./partials/shopping-cart') %>
  <%- include('./partials/product-quickview') %>
  <% if (!session.loggedIn) { %>
    <%- include('./partials/sign-up-modal') %>
    <%- include('./partials/sign-in-modal') %>
  <% } %>

  <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.3/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"
    integrity="sha384-YvpcrYf0tY3lHB60NNkmXc5s9fDVZLESaAA55NDzOxhy9GkcIdslK1eN7N6jIeHz"
    crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
  <script type="module" src="/assets/scripts/privacy.js"></script>
</body>

</html>
